Description: The URI can be used to join the conference

The URI can be used to access the streamed  
conference data

The URI can be used to subscribe to the     
conference event package

The URI can be used to access the recorded  
conference data

The URI can be used to access a web page   
that contains additional information of
the conference

The URI can be used to indicate that the   
conference focus supports CCMP.

The URI can be used to join a multi-user chat directly 
associated with the conference
